{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"44d1744cb1","title":"陈毅给“对外文委”的指示","origin":"刊载于《中央首长讲话》（3），北京玻璃总厂红卫兵联络站编，1967年4月。","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"9ce636fac8","index":0,"year":1967,"month":3,"day":17,"articleId":"44d1744cb1"}],"tags":[{"id":"0b2012c0b4","name":"革命三结合","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"1ae024ca96","name":"革命大联合","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"1feb996ca7","name":"陈毅","type":"人物"},{"id":"2d13338754","name":"指示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"4206ce6bf3","name":"红卫兵运动","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"aa048f8141","name":"夺权","type":"主题/事件"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"GPCRv3","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第三版）","internal":true,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"22f5bd1aa6","name":"陈毅"}]},"publication_details":{"GPCRv3":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"d9d9b7bccc","type":"title","text":"陈毅给“对外文委”的指示","index":0,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"44d1744cb1"},{"id":"1359b41df5","type":"authors","text":"陈毅","index":1,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"44d1744cb1"},{"id":"dda30da435","type":"paragraph","text":"1．二外红卫兵到对外文委夺权大方向是正确的。","index":2,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"44d1744cb1"},{"id":"676efff859","type":"paragraph","text":"2．按3月13日四单位会议纪要办事，立即成立个临时权力机构，这个机构有权领导文化大革命，并进行业务监督。","index":3,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"44d1744cb1"},{"id":"ff63354f70","type":"paragraph","text":"3．委、司干部暂不参加，待条件成熟时再搞三结合。","index":4,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"44d1744cb1"},{"id":"fbe12761d5","type":"paragraph","text":"4．同意两大战斗组织不单独派代表参加临时权力机构。","index":5,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"44d1744cb1"},{"id":"2a58be0490","type":"paragraph","text":"5．临时权力机构成立后，即领导全委战斗组织整风，整风后再搞大联合、三结合，逐步完善、充实，成为真正的三结合的权力机构。","index":6,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"44d1744cb1"},{"id":"238afc0d68","type":"paragraph","text":"6．贵阳经验很好，但要经过长期工作。各战斗组织不要强制解散，到能够实行按部门联合时，再根据自愿原则取消战斗组。","index":7,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"44d1744cb1"},{"id":"436dc3206e","type":"paragraph","text":"7．二外同学可按规定离委，交权不开大会。","index":8,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"44d1744cb1"},{"id":"6e9a45af76","type":"paragraph","text":"8．必须照顾大局，有关方面都要履行今晚的协议，在整风前各单位不互相攻击。","index":9,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"44d1744cb1"},{"id":"0b466da725","type":"paragraph","text":" 刊载于《中央首长讲话》（3），北京玻璃总厂红卫兵联络站编，1967年4月。","index":10,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"44d1744cb1"}],"page":{"id":"902566fc38","publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"44d1744cb1","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}